reviewText: This DVD I waited and watched for for years!  I love this movie!  Jill Eikenberry and Michael Tucker are great together in all the movies they have made together.

This movie starts out slow,  and looks very cheap,  Jill Eilenberry over acts in beginning,  but the movie picks up steam and has a great ending  about 20 mins in to movie they seem to relax  all and all it  I enjoyed the movie once it got going.
